Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\bord0\pos(319,227)\fs25\frz5}小熊紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬 冬眠前的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要先把肚子填飽才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 所以我要把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦 現在裝死也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始於去年的聖誕節的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼戀愛的少年與靦腆的少女的初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演 拍得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 冬眠前的感覺更加傳神一點就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再拍一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 在過了十個月之後的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的感情仍在茁壯成長中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:14.88,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:21.30,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:29.24,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:33.83,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:35.56,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.64,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:42.62,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:48.05,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:51.12,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.15,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.61,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:00.60,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:05.95,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:13.73,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.80,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.77,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.20,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
